    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Taiji 2.0"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Taiji 2.0 platform will support Aurix IDC Platform with Both Cubas and Vector solution."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The platform modules can work with both Vector and Cubas stack"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "For more detail status on Taiji 2.0 please refer this wiki Aurix - China Convergence - CUBAS solution - XC-CT China - Docupedia (bosch.com)"
    },
